  "response_text": "The commercial opens in a green park shaded by enormous old trees with wide trunks and dense leaves. Small groups of people stroll across the grass in pale clothing, spread out beneath the branches in a calm, public garden setting. The view moves closer to two babies or toddlers seated side by side in a pram or carriage. Both wear matching navy-and-white sailor outfits with broad white collars and white sailor caps edged in dark trim. One child is seen mostly from behind, while the other, a fair-skinned baby with rosy cheeks, faces sideways toward the first child, sitting upright against the cream-colored side of the carriage.\n\nThe peaceful mood gives way to a muddy outdoor sports scene. Men in athletic clothing rush across a grassy field, some in dark jerseys and others in yellow tops. A fair-haired male player in a dark, mud-streaked jersey clutches an oval ball against his body while opponents close in. He drops or slides down into the wet grass, bracing himself with his hands as another player in yellow lunges toward him. Mud and water splash up around his legs and torso, emphasizing the roughness of the play.\n\nThe setting changes to a quiet river or canal bordered by reeds and old brick buildings. A narrow rowboat sits low on the water. Two people are aboard: one, wearing a cap, handles an oar near the middle or rear of the boat, while another sits toward the front, facing him. The water reflects the warm light and the dark shapes of the buildings and banks.\n\nA group of schoolchildren then runs out from the entrance of an old stone or brick building with steps, statues of lions on either side, and a formal, historic look. The children wear dark school uniforms with white shirts and ties; many have straw boater hats. Several carry cricket bats, and one child in front lifts a bat high while running forward with an open-mouthed, excited expression. More uniformed children stream down the steps behind, filling the courtyard.\n\nA large United Airlines jet appears above a vast blanket of clouds glowing peach and gold. The aircraft is a wide-body, four-engine plane with a raised upper-deck hump near the front. It is white with a broad red-orange and gold stripe along the lower fuselage. As it turns, the word “UNITED” becomes clearly visible in large letters on the side, and the United tail emblem appears on the vertical fin. The plane glides steadily through the warm light, shown from the front and then more from the side, floating above the cloud tops.\n\nThe imagery returns to English scenery. A calm river or pond fills the foreground, reflecting bare-branched trees and a tall church or chapel tower on the far bank. A small boat rests near the left bank among reeds and grassy edges, and the scene feels still and rural or village-like. This dissolves into a cottage garden overflowing with flowers and greenery. An elderly woman with short white hair, wearing a light-colored dress and apron, stands beside a brick wall and a window framed by climbing plants. She holds purple flowers in her hands and faces the window and garden beds, surrounded by dense blooms in purple, white, red, and green.\n\nThe view shifts to a high, sweeping landscape of white coastal cliffs dropping sharply to a dark shoreline and sea. The cliffs run into the distance beneath a purple-pink sky, with grassy green land stretching along the top and a small structure visible on a hill near the horizon. Finally, London’s Houses of Parliament and the clock tower known as Big Ben appear from above beside the River Thames. The clock tower rises prominently in the foreground, with the long Gothic buildings and spires extending behind it. The river shimmers beside the complex, with boats visible on the water and traffic moving along the roads below.",
